From: ekane bryan <ekanebryan5@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 22 Jul 2026 12:54:03 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: subtle page animations across the app (Framer Motion)

Add a cohesive, professional animation layer:
- PageOutlet: every routed page fades + slides up on navigation
  (GuestLayout, AuthLayout, AppShell cover all routes)
- EventGrid / RecommendedEventsGrid: staggered card entrances
- SectionHeader: gentle scroll-reveal on every section
- HomePage: staggered category cards
- Button: subtle press feedback (whileTap) app-wide
- MotionConfig reducedMotion="user" respects prefers-reduced-motion
- Shared variants.js, Reveal and Stagger helpers for reuse
Build passes.
